HEADWORD: Quindecone
<hw>Quin*dec"one</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quindecim</ets> fifteen.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>An
unsaturated hydrocarbon, <chform>C15H26</chform>, of the valylene
series, produced artificially as an oily liquid.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>quindekone</asp>.]</altsp><-- now quindecene??-->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

